title: Spacious Bedroom, Large Closet & Off-Street Parking - 2 Weeks Free
posting_body: ['Eastlake 1 Bedroom - 2 Weeks Free Rent!', 'Property Address', '2840 EASTLAKE AVE E UNIT 617 | SEATTLE, WA 98102', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'South Coronado Apartments - Seattle Property Management Associates', 'Description', 'The Coronado Apartments is in the desirable Eastlake neighborhood on a main bus line to Downtown, South Lake Union, and the University of Washington.', 'The Eastlake neighborhood is home to lots of great places to eat within walking distance and is convenient to Interstate 5 for those who need to commute for work.', 'The Coronado features updated kitchens with new cabinets, granite countertops and Wood Floors.', 'The units have large closets and spacious bedrooms.', 'Off street parking may be available for a separate fee.', 'This unit is being offered on a 12-month Lease with $50 w,s,g fee and 2 weeks free rent!', 'At the time of application, we require payment of the $25 application fee per person and a $1000 deposit that is then applied to the refundable security deposit upon approval.', 'This building is no smoking and no dogs, cats are allowed.', 'Photos of similar unit.', 'For more information or to make an appointment to tour, contact us at', 'show contact info', 'Feel free to view all of our property vacancies at: <URL>/', 'Amenities', 'On-Site Management', 'Laundry On Site', 'Controlled Access', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 470', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,495.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
